    SiteSubnets = Site Subnets
    Subnet = Subnet
    NoSiteAssigned = No site assigned
    SubnetSiteBP = Ensure Subnets have an associated site. If subnets are not associated with AD Sites, users in the AD Sites might choose a remote domain controller for authentication. This can lead to increased latency and potential performance issues for users authenticating against a domain controller that is not local to their site.
    MissingSubnets = Missing Subnets in AD
